title: 1935 Western - Wagon Trail - Framed for Crime, Fighting for Justice: A Sheriff’s Last Stand

sources.title: 1935 Western - Wagon Trail - Framed for Crime, Fighting for Justice: A Sheriff’s Last Stand
sources.description:
Sheriff Clay Hartley's son, from the frontier town of Elder, has fallen into bad company and joined an outlaw gang secretly led by Collins, the owner of the Golden Rule Saloon.

Main Cast:
Harry Carey - Sheriff Clay Hartley
Gertrude Messinger - Joan Collins
Edward Norris - Clay Hartley, Jr.
Roger Williams - Mark Collins
Earl Dwire - Deputy Joe Larkin
Chuck Morrison - Deputy Chuck
John Elliott - Judge
Chief Thundercloud - Henchman
Lew Meehan - Henchman
Barney Beasley - Henchman
Tex Palmer - Henchman

Directed by Harry L. Fraser

B&W version: https://youtu.be/YK2vFd3zu4c
